{"tid":937763,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"真心覺得香港人好多野都要考返個牌先","createTime":"2018-12-11T19:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T14:21:43.000Z","uid":79566,"like":94,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4889506d50d165821def5bd070b0366be1591a4e","tid":937763,"uid":79566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:56:32.000Z","msg":"尤其係無腦自私撚<br />\n<br />\n地鐵入閘:<br />\n試拎定個銀包出黎先？<br />\n入唔到試下讓俾人先<br />\n屌你老母見唔見到成條龍？<br />\n<br />\n撘地鐵:<br />\n仆街自私撚試下企入啲？<br />\n放低你個臭系書包同㩒小一兩個站電話啦<br />\n撞撚到你又要嘴喵喵<br />\n仲有啲死廢老，中年啊姐，以為自己好苗條？<br />\n仲逼入黎呀？下一班車啦屌你個系，一個側身逼返你出去<br />\n<br />\n叫野食:<br />\n試下諗好左先叫個侍應個黎？<br />\n哎完凍檸茶人地準備走個下先話<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span>都係唔好，要熱檸水吖<br />\n又唔撚識聽人講野？<br />\n十個人叫ABCD餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 侍應<br />\n幾多個要A餐呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要C餐吖<br />\n飲咩野？<br />\n十個一齊講 凍熱檸奶小茶冰啡甜走乜乜乜<br />\n人地點聽呀？<br />\n啲野食到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 凍檸茶小甜小冰邊個？<br />\n冇人應，個個㩒電話傾計<br />\n<br />\n中學雞都算，廿尻幾歲人都係咁<br />\n食殺利亞<br />\n㩒完鐘仔先諗食乜<br />\n大佬呀，人地俾你叫狗咁叫埋黎就係睇住你諗食乜？<br />\n<br />\n不過有啲野有牌都冇撚用<br />\n你睇啲撚屌揸車<br />\n打燈啦仆街<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人。瞓撚醒未呀？"},{"pid":"513af6824a50457573afea820b4207dd8b761e8b","tid":937763,"uid":55636,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:59:59.000Z","msg":"仲有女人擔遮要考牌呢"},{"pid":"90d4bf5b672d80cc5bc34a3f29fbb94f685247b3","tid":937763,"uid":1655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"513af6824a50457573afea820b4207dd8b761e8b","tid":937763,"uid":55636,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:59:59.000Z","msg":"仲有女人擔遮要考牌呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"行路同用atm都要"},{"pid":"168c24d16511c48e5a1762f3422e592e8ed336f6","tid":937763,"uid":79566,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:05:22.000Z","msg":"仲有落雨個陣:<br />\n擔住把傘個班臭系港女師奶，行到入有蓋又迫既行人路試下收返埋你把傘<br />\n<br />\n行街:<br />\n真係老人家同遊客(大陸人除外)<br />\n試下係旺角銅鑼灣唔好行行下停低？<br />\n我自己有需要例如要企係到睇一睇個電玩，甩鞋帶，都會係個岩既timing 望一望後面有冇人先囉好冇？"},{"pid":"33ae21a35b9fd28b9e8fab61436904e4e8bd0fec","tid":937763,"uid":79566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"513af6824a50457573afea820b4207dd8b761e8b","tid":937763,"uid":55636,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:59:59.000Z","msg":"仲有女人擔遮要考牌呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:06:47.000Z","msg":"正想講"},{"pid":"c91469f34e5ef173d959e879b4b15ba1aa09c3aa","tid":937763,"uid":79566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d4bf5b672d80cc5bc34a3f29fbb94f685247b3","tid":937763,"uid":1655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"513af6824a50457573afea820b4207dd8b761e8b","tid":937763,"uid":55636,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:59:59.000Z","msg":"仲有女人擔遮要考牌呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"行路同用atm都要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:07:06.000Z","msg":"正想講"},{"pid":"c6340051dea2a59dae6d008a4f62498b836f68ad","tid":937763,"uid":40087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:31:47.000Z","msg":"推到上報 中晒想屌嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ee4ceafc22df6217c56d0b00950a19aa551c23","tid":937763,"uid":40087,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"90d4bf5b672d80cc5bc34a3f29fbb94f685247b3","tid":937763,"uid":1655,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"513af6824a50457573afea820b4207dd8b761e8b","tid":937763,"uid":55636,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T19:59:59.000Z","msg":"仲有女人擔遮要考牌呢"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"行路同用atm都要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T23:33:33.000Z","msg":"不論男女老幼都見過 行到蟻躝咁 仲要行正路中心"},{"pid":"c24401aa0571c4f66a467a410a715160dccd43bc","tid":937763,"uid":59898,